epack - Evidence Pack Builder

Quick Start:

  # Create a new project
  epack new my-pipeline

  # Or initialize in existing directory
  epack init

  # Run collectors and build a pack
  epack collect

  # Sign the pack (opens browser for authentication)
  epack sign evidence.pack

  # Verify pack integrity and attestations
  epack verify evidence.pack

  # Push pack to a remote registry
  epack push locktivity evidence.pack

  # Pull pack from a remote registry
  epack pull locktivity

Commands:
  new        Create a new evidence pack project
  init       Initialize epack in current directory
  collect    Run collectors and build evidence pack
  install    Lock and sync dependencies
  lock       Lock collector and tool dependencies
  sync       Install collectors and tools from lockfile
  build      Build an evidence pack from artifacts
  sign       Sign an evidence pack
  verify     Verify pack integrity and attestations
  inspect    Show pack contents and metadata
  list       List pack artifacts, attestations, or sources
  extract    Extract artifacts from a pack
  merge      Merge multiple packs into one
  diff       Compare two packs
  push       Push pack to a remote registry
  pull       Pull pack from a remote registry
  status     Show project status
  jobs       List background jobs
  collector  Run collectors
  tool       Run tools on evidence packs

Run epack <command> --help for detailed usage.
